sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as DS Pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP REST<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant Pods as Pipeline Step Pods
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant S3 as S3 / MinIO<br/>9000/TCP or 443/TCP
    participant MLMD as MLMD GRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL

    Note over User,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Execution

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Route->>KRBAC: Reencrypt TLS<br/>443 → 8443
    KRBAC->>KRBAC: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(datasciencepipelinesapplications/api)
    KRBAC->>API: Forward to 8888/TCP<br/>HTTP (or HTTPS if PodToPodTLS)
    API->>DB: Store pipeline run metadata<br/>MySQL 3306/TCP, TLS optional<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    API->>Argo: Create Workflow CR<br/>Kubernetes API, TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Argo->>Pods: Create pipeline step pods<br/>Kubernetes API, TLS
    Pods->>S3: Upload/download artifacts<br/>9000/TCP or 443/TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+ (configurable)<br/>Auth: Access Key/Secret Key
    Pods->>MLMD: Record metadata<br/>gRPC 8080/TCP<br/>TLS optional (PodToPodTLS)
    MLMD->>DB: Store lineage data<br/>MySQL 3306/TCP<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    PA->>Argo: Watch Workflow status
    PA->>API: Sync execution state<br/>8888/8887 TCP<br/>TLS optional (PodToPodTLS)<br/>Auth: Projected SA token

    Note over User,DB: Flow 2: Managed Pipeline Import

    participant DSPO as DSPO Controller
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    DSPO->>OCI: Fetch pipeline manifest<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Registry credentials
    DSPO->>DSPO: Validate pipeline names<br/>against manifest
    Note over DSPO,API: Init container injected<br/>into API Server Deployment
    API->>API: Load managed pipelines<br/>from shared volume on startup

    Note over User,DB: Flow 3: MLMD Metadata Access

    participant Envoy as MLMD Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/TCP HTTP/2
    participant KRBAC2 as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    User->>Route: GET metadata<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Route->>KRBAC2: Reencrypt TLS<br/>443 → 8443
    KRBAC2->>KRBAC2: SubjectAccessReview
    KRBAC2->>Envoy: Forward to 9090/TCP<br/>HTTP/2 (gRPC-Web)
    Envoy->>MLMD: gRPC 8080/TCP<br/>TLS optional (PodToPodTLS)
    MLMD->>DB: Query lineage<br/>MySQL 3306/TCP<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    DB-->>MLMD: Results
    MLMD-->>Envoy: gRPC response
    Envoy-->>KRBAC2: HTTP/2 response
    KRBAC2-->>Route: HTTPS response
    Route-->>User: JSON/gRPC-Web response
